This article showcases news, blog posts, and updates that VRChat published between January 1, 2019 and December 31, 2019.
==History==

Since 2016, VRChat's developer updates have been posted on several outlets, and have also gone through different names. Former developer updates have been called ''Developer Blogs'', ''Community Updates'', and ''Town Hall Meetings''.

<br>Patch notes for VRChat ''Builds released in 2019<ref>[https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/patch-notes-2019 'Patch Notes - 2019' on Creator Docs; retrieved September 6, 2024.]</ref>'' can be viewed [https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/patch-notes-2019 here].
